#### This tutorial dscribes how to implement the carrier function in your shop system #### 

Please follow the steps exactly, elsewere the upgrade abort.

If you don't made any changes in the original templates, it's enough when you copy the new templates into the particular directory see below). 
Anyway, you have to copy the missing files and templates into the particular directory.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Following templates to have to castomize:

in \out\basic\tpl
account_order.tpl

in \out\admin\tpl
order_main.tpl

copying following files:

in \out\admin\tpl
carrer.tpl
carrier_list.tpl
carrier_main.tpl

in \admin

carrier.php
carrier_main.php
carrier_list.php
menu.xml

in \core

oxcarrierlist.php
oxcarrier.php

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To create a database table

To save and manage the carriers do you need in your database a further table (oxcarriertracking). It is also nassesary to add a field to the table 'oxorder' 

If you use phpmyadmin to administer your database, than follow the steps below:

1) Log on to phpmyadmin
2) Choose your database
3) Click the import rider 
4) Choose the provided file 'update.sql' and click than [OK] 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

account_order.tpl :

 Replace the line 54 
   <a href="http://www.dpd.de/cgi-bin/delistrack?typ=1&amp;lang=de&amp;pknr=[{ $order->oxorder__oxtrackcode->value }]">[{ oxmultilang ident="ACCOUNT_ORDER_TRACKSHIPMENT" }]</a>
   through
   <a href="[{$order->oxorder__oxtrackadr->value}][{ $order->oxorder__oxtrackcode->value }]" target="_blank">[{ oxmultilang ident="ACCOUNT_ORDER_TRACKSHIPMENT" }]</a>   
     
 account_order.tpl is customized.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
order_main.tpl :

 Insert 
    [{if $edit->oxorder__oxtrackcode->value}]
        <tr>
         <td class="edittext">
           [{ oxmultilang ident="GENERAL_CARRIER" }]
         </td>
         <td class="edittext">
          <select class="editinput" name="editval[oxorder__oxtrackadr]" [{ $readonly }]>
            [{ foreach from=$carrierlist item=oCarrier}]
            <option value="[{$oCarrier->oxcarriertracking__oxtrackadr->value}]" [{if $oCarrier->oxcarriertracking__oxtrackadr->value == $edit->oxorder__oxtrackadr->value}]selected[{/if}]>[{$oCarrier->oxcarriertracking__oxtitle->value}]</option>
            [{/foreach}]
          </select>
         </td>
        </tr>
    [{/if}]
  between the lines of the tracking code and shipping costs		   

 order_main.tpl is customized.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
menu.xml :

 Insert 
    <SUBMENU id="mxcarriertrack" cl="carrier" list="carrier_list">
      <TAB id="tbclcarrier_main" cl="carrier_main" />
      <BTN id="carrier_new" />
    </SUBMENU>
  between the lines 17 and 18.	
	
	menu.xml is cusomized.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  
\admin\de\cust_lang.php

  Insert into the array following language constants:  	
  
	'GENERAL_CARRIER'			=> 'Spediteur',
	'CARRIER_LIST_TITLE'    	=> '[OXID Speditionsverwaltung]',
	'GENERAL_TRACK_TITLE'		=> 'Spediteur',
	'TOOLTIPS_NEWCARRIER'		=> 'Neuen Spediteur anlegen',
	'CARRIER_MAIN_ICONUPLOAD'	=> 'Spediteut-Icon hochladen',
	'CARRIER_LIST_MENUITEM'		=> 'Shopeinstellungen',
	'CARRIER_LIST_MENUSUBITEM'	=> 'Spediteure',

# menu

	'mxcarriertrack'			=> 'Spediteure',
  
# tabs

	// Carrier
	'tbclcarrier_main'			=> 'Stamm', 		
	
